<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Registro Completo - Cuidamor</title>
  <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .form-signin-container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin: auto;
      background-color: white;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .header img {
      height: 70px;
    }

    .back-button {
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      left: 10px;
    }

    .back-button img {
      height: 40px;
    }

    .list-group {
      text-align: left;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 15px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .thank-you-message {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <img src="imgs/logo.png" alt="Cuidamor Logo">
  </div>
  <div class="form-signin-container">
    <h1 class="h3 mb-3 font-weight-normal">Registro Completo</h1>
    <p class="thank-you-message">¡Felicidades! Has completado el registro inicial.</p>
    <p>Para continuar con tu registro, necesitarás subir los siguientes documentos:</p>
    <ul class="list-group">
      <li class="list-group-item">Cédula Profesional</li>
      <li class="list-group-item">Certificados</li>
      <li class="list-group-item">Comprobante de Identidad Vigente </li>
      <li class="list-group-item">Comprobante de Domicilio</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Para proseguir con el registro, por favor <strong>inicia sesión</strong> y sigue las instrucciones.</p>
    <button class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" onclick="location.href='/Iniciar_sesion'">Iniciar Sesión</button>
  </div>
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
